{"tid":1995210,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"台中防疫廣告激似 AV 封面？結果引出 AV 女優上原亞衣回應","createTime":"2020-04-30T05:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T06:24:09.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8ca7ded95c059b4ee10d2473ac6f53d9ab296582","tid":1995210,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:30:14.000Z","msg":"台灣在新冠肺炎的防疫工作上，做出驚人的成果，多個國家也稱要參考借鏡。最近，台中市一張新刊登的新冠肺炎防疫海報，也超級爆紅，當中海報可見一位露出肚臍戴上口罩逃跑的美女，正被一群男警追趕著，而下方則寫道「居家隔離者擅離者，罰款 20 萬 - 100 萬」。之不過，這與昔日當紅 AV 女優上原亞衣的引退作品「100 人中出」的封面，卻十分激似。<br />\n<br />\n事件在台灣亦引起網民的熱烈討論，而台中市就解釋，海報的創作意念來自日本綜藝節目「全員逃走中」。之不過，最意外的是這海報竟熱傳至日本當中，更引得 AV 女優上原亞衣來個「掩咀偷笑」的 emoji 回覆，讓網民們紛紛派心及 share 呢！"},{"pid":"acd6246d56ac7bf6f4de73467e84d2b6f5829812","tid":1995210,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2630000/2631411/200429_uehsrs_00_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2630000%2F2631411%2F200429_uehsrs_00_1024.jpg&h=1cc37a42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8044e29bcf31cab3f3b20cc06fbf98ca4b605945","tid":1995210,"uid":16659,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2630000/2631411/200429_uehsrs_01_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2630000%2F2631411%2F200429_uehsrs_01_600.jpg&h=1842ad16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n引得上原亞衣本尊親自回覆。"},{"pid":"671b81ccf8dc9b5c5532aeb4424853038624f930","tid":1995210,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T05:32:23.000Z","msg":"阿姨仲有冇出新片?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1058c1c9da98e3ff7d5510c9c95a8bec998ea2","tid":1995210,"uid":16659,